column5: Lol my life is always shit
Age 19, started collage, i am once again diagnosed with depression
I just want everything to stop. Doesn't matter how much i try it always gets worse. When i was younger i wanted life that i am living today but there's always something that comes up to ruin it all
I'm now laughing in the train, this shit continues
I can feel you, a girl i used to hang out with gat mad at me for some reason and now she just completely ignores me... Don't know what to. Pain just keeps growing
I don't even wanna be happy, i just don't wanna feel so bad all the time

I feel you too, i just don't understand what do i have to do in this life. Don't wanna take it either but fuck man i really don't like the world around me. If i do everything right then something bad happens, if nothing bad happens for a while i manage to fuck something up... Can't live it, can't escape it. Somethimes i think this is the afterlife and im in hell
